OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fwill clear away this evening. The rest
OL,7,Fof the night will be dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells, perhaps more cloud affecting
OL,9,Fthe Glasgow area later on.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FDry and settled with light
OL,12,Fwinds. Any early morning cloud will
OL,13,Fbreak up to leave a good deal of warm
OL,14,Fsunshine for the rest of the day.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,17,Fand settled conditions prevail through
OL,18,Fthis period, with light winds and
OL,19,Fplenty of sunshine. A chance of a few
OL,20,Fshowers on Friday. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
